    {
      "type": "narrator_en",
      "text": "Welcome to lesson five of PolishPod. In this lesson you will learn to talk about spring weather, flowers, and plan outdoor activities with a friend. You will also learn a very natural Polish expression for saying you feel like doing something. Listen carefully to the following conversation between a man and a woman meeting on a spring morning in Warsaw."
